File::Locate::Iterator reads a "locate" database file, similar to
what File::Locate does, but done as an iterator rather than callbacks.

The module can be used natively, or there's optional support for
Iterator.pm, Iterator::Simple and MooseX::Iterator style iterators.

The File-Locate-Iterator home page is

    http://user42.tuxfamily.org/file-locate-iterator/index.html
